  "description": "<p>据国外媒体报道，法国著名设计师弗朗科伊斯·瑞巴茨克（Francois Rybarczyk）又构思出了一款iPhone充电外壳<strong>，取名为Juice up，它可以在你的iPhone电量即将耗尽，又找不到充电电源的情况下，像一根电缆一样接入另外一部iPhone并获取电量。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb3d39a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244774.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84iPhone%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244774.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84iPhone%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244774.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84iPhone%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244774.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84iPhone%E5%A4%96%E5%A3%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244774.htm&amp;t=%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%87%E7%94%A8%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84iPhon